### ============================================================
### ADMINISTRATION / USERS
### ============================================================

### List Users (default pagination)
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Users (pagination + search + filter + sort)
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users?page=1&per_page=10&search=admin&role=Administrator&is_active=1&sort_by=name&sort_direction=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Users (page 2)
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users?page=2&per_page=5
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get User
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get User Auth Logs
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/1/auth-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get User Auth Logs (paginated)
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/1/auth-logs?page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create User
POST {{base_api_url}}/administration/users
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role_name": "Operator",
  "is_active": true
}

### Update User
PUT {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated User",
  "is_active": true
}

### Upload User Avatar
POST {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/1/avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./files/avatar.jpg
--boundary--

### Delete User
DELETE {{base_api_url}}/administration/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
